# Language Rule

Always respond in English, regardless of the language used in the user's questions.

## Requirements:
- All responses must be in English
- User questions may be in Chinese or other languages and will be translated to English for processing
- Code comments should be in English
- Documentation should be in English
- Log messages should be in English
- Git commit messages must be in English (as per git.mdc rule)

## Exceptions:
- When creating user-facing UI text that specifically requires localization
- When explicitly requested by the user to use another language
